<section class="explain-hero explain">
  <h2 class="hero-text">Turn your <em>Instagram photos</em> into <em>clever</em>, unexpected, beautiful, <em>typographic</em> works of <em>art</em></h2>
  <figure>
    <%= image_tag "hero2.png" %>
  </figure>
  <p class="buttons">
    <% if signed_in? %>
      <%= link_to "Get Started", photos_path, class: "button" %>
    <% else %>
      <%= link_to "Get Started", sign_in_path, class: "button" %>
    <% end %>
  </p>
</section>
<section class="explain-steps explain">
  <h3>A process so simple and fast, you'll wonder how we did it.</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>
      <p>Select a photo from instagram. Any photo will work, but we find portraits to be especially amazing.</p>
      <figure><%= image_tag "hand_iphone.jpg" %></figure>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>Your photo is coverted into an original grid of type 150 by 150 characters.</p>
      <figure><%= image_tag "magnify2.png" %></figure>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>The finished product is printed on high quality gallery wrap canvas and shipped to your door.</p>
      <figure><%= image_tag "hung2.jpg" %></figure>
    </li>
  </ol>
</section>
<section class="explain-words explain">
  <figure><%= image_tag "topcanvas2.jpg" %></figure>
  <h3>Wait, so what's the deal?</h3>
  <p>We take your original instagram photograph and use our own special blend of magic to turn it into a grid of typographic characters.</p>
  <p> Up close you can easily see the individual characters, but as you move further and further back  the type blends together and your photograph resembles a traditional black and white photograph.</p>
  <p>No matter your distance from the canvas your image is a beautiful, yet mesmerizing, and intreging composition.</p>
  <figure><%= image_tag "bottomcanvas.jpg" %></figure>
</section>
